---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn more about Paul - Co-Founder & CTO building AI Edge Devices and Computer Vision solutions.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Hero with avatar -->
    <section class="pixel-border p-8 mb-8" style="background: var(--color-cream);">
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-8">
        <!-- Pixel avatar -->
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 pixel-border flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--color-bread);">
            <img
              src="/images/pixel-avatar.svg"
              alt="Paul's pixel avatar"
              class="w-24 h-24 pixel-render"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center sm:text-left">
          <h1 class="font-pixel text-base" style="color: var(--color-brown-dark);">About Me</h1>
          <p class="mt-2" style="color: var(--color-brown);">
            Co-Founder & CTO with 10+ years in software engineering
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="pixel-border p-8" style="background: var(--color-cream);">
      <article class="prose prose-pixel max-w-none">
        <p>
          Hey, I'm <strong>Paul</strong> - Co-Founder & CTO with 10+ years of experience
          in software engineering.
        </p>

        <h2>What I Do</h2>

        <p>Currently, I'm focused on:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>AI Edge Devices</strong> - Building computer vision solutions that run 24/7</li>
          <li><strong>Scrapee Labs</strong> - Running an AI & automation agency at <a href="https://scrapeelabs.com">scrapeelabs.com</a></li>
          <li><strong>WordPress Plugins</strong> - Maintaining products with 40K+ active installs</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Tech Stack</h2>

        <p>My go-to technologies:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> React, TypeScript, Node.js</li>
          <li><strong>Backend:</strong> Python (FastAPI), PHP, Node.js</li>
          <li><strong>DevOps:</strong> AWS, Docker, PostgreSQL, Redis</li>
          <li><strong>Current interests:</strong> Edge AI, MCP servers, distributed systems</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Why This Blog</h2>

        <p>
          I believe in documenting lessons learned - both wins and mistakes. This blog is where
          I share practical insights from building products, debugging tricky issues, and
          navigating the startup journey.
        </p>

        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>

        <p>
          Feel free to reach out if you're working on something interesting or just want to chat
          about AI, startups, or software engineering.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
